languages.text: "Элантах, и ты здесь! Помоги, скорей же. Нужно спасти его, пока не вернулись надсмотрщики. Где-то в комнате должен быть переключатель, смотри внимательней".

traits.locale_text: "Элантах, и ты здесь! Помоги, скорей же. Нужно спасти его, пока не вернулись надсмотрщики. Где-то в комнате должен быть переключатель, смотри внимательней".

languages.text: "You are here too, elantach! Quick, help me. We must save him before the guards return. There should be a switch somewhere in this room. Look carefully."

languages.text: «¡Tú también estás aquí, elantach! Rápido, ayúdame. Hemos de liberarlo antes de que vuelvan los guardias. Debería haber un interruptor en algún lugar de esta sala. Busca a fondo».
languages.original_text: "You are here too, elantach! Quick, help me. We must save him before the guards return. There should be a switch somewhere in this room. Look carefully."

traits.locale_text: «¡Tú también estás aquí, elantach! Rápido, ayúdame. Hemos de liberarlo antes de que vuelvan los guardias. Debería haber un interruptor en algún lugar de esta sala. Busca a fondo».

languages.text: 「あなたもいたのだな、エランタ！さあ、早く助けてくれ。衛兵たちが戻る前に彼を救い出さねば。この部屋のどこかにスイッチがあるはずだ。よく見てくれ」
languages.original_text: "You are here too, elantach! Quick, help me. We must save him before the guards return. There should be a switch somewhere in this room. Look carefully."

traits.locale_text: 「あなたもいたのだな、エランタ！さあ、早く助けてくれ。衛兵たちが戻る前に彼を救い出さねば。この部屋のどこかにスイッチがあるはずだ。よく見てくれ」

languages.text: “你也在这里，外界人！快来，帮帮我，我们必须赶在守卫回来之前把他救出来。这个房间里应该有个开关才对，仔细找找。”
languages.original_text: "You are here too, elantach! Quick, help me. We must save him before the guards return. There should be a switch somewhere in this room. Look carefully."

traits.locale_text: “你也在这里，外界人！快来，帮帮我，我们必须赶在守卫回来之前把他救出来。这个房间里应该有个开关才对，仔细找找。”

languages.text: « Vous voilà aussi, elantach ! Vite, aidez-moi. Nous devons le sauver avant le retour des gardes. Il devrait y avoir un interrupteur quelque part dans la pièce. Cherchez bien. »
languages.original_text: "You are here too, elantach! Quick, help me. We must save him before the guards return. There should be a switch somewhere in this room. Look carefully."

traits.locale_text: « Vous voilà aussi, elantach ! Vite, aidez-moi. Nous devons le sauver avant le retour des gardes. Il devrait y avoir un interrupteur quelque part dans la pièce. Cherchez bien. »

languages.text: "Ihr seid ja auch hier, Elantach! Schnell, helft mir. Wir müssen ihn retten, bevor die Wachen zurückkommen. Irgendwo hier im Raum muss es einen Schalter geben. Sucht alles ab."
languages.original_text: "You are here too, elantach! Quick, help me. We must save him before the guards return. There should be a switch somewhere in this room. Look carefully."

traits.locale_text: "Ihr seid ja auch hier, Elantach! Schnell, helft mir. Wir müssen ihn retten, bevor die Wachen zurückkommen. Irgendwo hier im Raum muss es einen Schalter geben. Sucht alles ab."

languages.text: "Sen de buradasın elantach! Çabuk, bana yardım et. Muhafızlar dönmeden onu kurtarmalıyız. Odanın bir yerlerinde şalter olacak. Etrafa dikkatlice bakın."
languages.original_text: "You are here too, elantach! Quick, help me. We must save him before the guards return. There should be a switch somewhere in this room. Look carefully."

traits.locale_text: "Sen de buradasın elantach! Hadi, hemen bana yardım et. Muhafızlar dönmeden onu kurtarmalıyız. Odanın bir yerlerinde bir şalter olacak. Etrafa dikkatlice bakın."
